Name: Super SplashTube Bros.
About the game: A physics-based fighting game where the characters are disguised versions of some cool Brazilian YouTubers. Choose your favorite YouTuber and fight to show who's the greatest. This is a fighting game with 3D graphics but you can move in only two dimensions. It's super simple to play: just choose one out of the 8 available characters and go into a quest to beat all the others in their respective home arenas. To win a fight, simply push your opponent out of the arena. Features 8 amazing fighters (that you might know) 8 epic battle arenas A lot of ragdoll physics Super simple controls: just walk, jump and punch (a lot) Controls WASD keys to move F to punch (connect multiple attacks for combos) Hold F to block attacks Space bar to jump
